                <p>For press releases and news, contact <a href="mailto:press@pdfshift.io">press@pdfshift.io</a>.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="details">
                <h2>Who are we?</h2>

                <p>
                    PDFShift.io provides a powerful API to convert any HTML documents to high-fidelity PDF.
                    Its focus is in providing a fast and simple - but complete - API that allow any developers to setup their system in a few minutes.
                    The quick learning curve, the simplicity of the API and the quality of the result is what makes PDFShift a leader in the current market for Web-to-PDF conversions API.
                </p>

                <p>
                    PDFShift's is a French company created by Cyril Nicodeme and is located in
                    <address>
                    <strong>PDFShift SAS</strong><br />
                    30 rue de la claichiere<br />
                    2nd floor<br />
                    90800 BAVILLIERS<br />
                    France
                    </address>
                </p>

                <p>For all Press related inquiry, we recommend you to contact our marketing team at <a href="mailto:press@pdfshift.io" title="Contact our marketing team">press@pdfshift.io</a> or directly via our <a href="/contact/" title="Use our contact form">contact form</a>.</p>
